targets.query:
from(bucket: "telemetry-2023-11-05-Racebox")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "gps")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["ID"] == "gps_position")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "latitude" or r["_field"] == "longitude")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: $__interval, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "telemetry-2023-11-05-Racebox")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "lap_times")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "best_lap_number" or r["_field"] == "best_time" or r["_field"] == "lap_counter" or r["_field"] == "last_time")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["lap_time"] == "best" or r["lap_time"] == "best_lap_number" or r["lap_time"] == "lap_number" or r["lap_time"] == "last")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean)

from(bucket: "telemetry-2023-11-05")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "damp")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["ID"] == "6")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "angle")

total_number = () => {
  row = from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
    |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
    |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "damp")
    |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "position_rebound")
    |> filter(fn: (r) => r["ID"] == "7")
    |> count()  
    |> last() 
    |> findRecord(fn: (key) => true, idx:0)
  return float(v: row._value)
    
}


from(bucket: "${bucketName}")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "damp")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "position_rebound")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["ID"] == "7")
  |> duplicate(column: "_value", as: "new_column")
  |> group(columns: ["new_column"])
  |> count()
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({r with _value: float(v: r._value) /total_number() * 100.0}))
